{"tid":1430590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"七夕觀星有感***","createTime":"2019-08-07T19:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T01:47:21.000Z","uid":298663,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dcaad9cb31e6a07d3ad132ad12b1eeb3c6cf7fbb","tid":1430590,"uid":298663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:04:45.000Z","msg":"原本放工好攰無諗住去觀星又傳會取消<br />\n但最後都係去左睇下<br />\n結果真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩個月黎睇住場運動變化<br />\n和班非遊行定發夢都有試過<br />\n但近呢幾次發夢都感受到部分手足開始有少少失控<br />\n真係仇恨上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似隨時開拖咁<br />\n當然好明白好嬲<br />\n但係冇禮貌既問題愈黎愈嚴重（開口就dllm)<br />\n同埋幾個打一個串77(唔抵幫)既廢老<br />\n咁樣真係點都有啲反感<br />\n又係矇哂面去私下了結好似同克警冇咩分別<br />\n唔係想割蓆 打死都唔割<br />\n但真心希望要對返準槍頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心態好緊要<br />\n<br />\n但係今晚大家企出黎<br />\n係為左顯示班克警幾無能同荒謬<br />\n原意本來唔係為左玩！<br />\n但真係好開心好感動啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔洗擔心有人同記者受傷<br />\n唔洗戴住口罩 做返自己<br />\n唔洗聽到粗聲粗氣叫人唔好影相<br />\n唔洗再驚有克警清場<br />\n唔洗再打打鬧鬧<br />\n</span><br />\n「鐳射槍」射出黎啲激光好靚<br />\n我見到好多香港人都笑得好開心<br />\n遊客都玩得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時真係達到我地嘅目的<br />\n真係好愛你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場扙唔易打<br />\n有排打<br />\n我地如果下下硬碰硬<br />\n一定好快玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望日後用多啲創意智取啦<br />\n好愛你地！<br />\n一定要贏啊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人加油 堅持五大訴求</span>"},{"pid":"a3a1731caacae1f97d2fb2b4ad4fd0aa352dfa48","tid":1430590,"uid":298663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:07:24.000Z","msg":"唔好戀戰啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地係要贏！"},{"pid":"219c1911d34c17e1ea54000849925175a24dc2cc","tid":1430590,"uid":97840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:16:43.000Z","msg":"我都有去，希望再有下一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435fa02bf59988fba1633be5ce3c818fc9e7b124","tid":1430590,"uid":298663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"219c1911d34c17e1ea54000849925175a24dc2cc","tid":1430590,"uid":97840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:16:43.000Z","msg":"我都有去，希望再有下一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:24:25.000Z","msg":"仲有好長既路要行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e904c00f5903e144ec6ba9416b3427604787de2","tid":1430590,"uid":99582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:26:33.000Z","msg":"最開心係竟然唔洗戴口罩同上GEAR 可以同成班唔識既香港人 一齊玩 真係未試過<br />\n仲要我已經都唔算後生 都玩得好開心"},{"pid":"d48448fb61c49f564cf2a5cfdc47713c5fd5b49f","tid":1430590,"uid":253461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"有個記者講左句野 我喊到仆街<br />\n佢話元朗個日佢冇去到 冇好好保護你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCLS架 希望記者朋友們係琴晚屬於我地香港人既disco night 玩得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}